address.streetAddress: 321 S Martin Luther King Jr Ave

location.fullValue: 321 S Martin Luther King Jr Ave

data.description: Ideal property for independent self employed ,plenty of space for landscaping,construction, mechanic or daycare! This house is perfect for you and your business! Come to see this beautiful ranch home that offers: 3 bedrooms, 2.5 Bathrooms, and 2 garages (2.5 attached garage fits 2 cars & a detached garage fits 3 cars). Spacious master bedroom with full bathroom and access to the deck. The 2.5 bathrooms & kitchen are remodeled, complete with stainless steel appliances and beautiful hardwood floors. The family room is enormous great for entertaining. The property is fenced. Newer furnace & hot water 50 gallons. Newer electrical, windows, doors, light fixtures, roof & siding. The property has a half acre, so you have plenty of space to park your trucks. This home is unique, don't miss this opportunity. Schedule a viewing today!
